text: Joanna Leanna García (born August 10, 1979) is an American actress. She acts mostly on television. She has also been in some movies. She played Cheyenne Hart Montgomery in the sitcom Reba. She played Mia Putney in the sitcom Better with You. García was born in Tampa, Florida. Category:Actors from Florida Category:American television actors Category:1979 births Category:Living people
title: Joanna García
